data.description: LIKE NEW: HIGHLY DESIRABLE RIDGE LINE MODEL ON A PREMIUM VIEW LOT, WITH NO NEIGHBORS BEHIND, AMAZING MOUNTAIN AND SUNSET VIEWS. $100K THE BACKYARD includes a custom waterfall with spa-like features, built-in BBQ with hightop bar, travertine pavers, pet friendly artificial grass and landscape lighting. Located in the prestigious community of Northpointe and walking distance to the community center. This David Weekly home offers a grand entrance, designer appointed 8x39'' plank tile flooring, wide hallways, stunning chef's kitchen w/GE stainless appliances, white & charcoal shaker cabinets,upgraded quartz countertops, island w/sink, breakfast bar and eat-in-kitchen open to the Great room where abundant natural light soar thru large picturesque windows highlighting the 10-12' ceilings throughout.The Owners suite offers a spa-like bathroom with a stunning walk-in rain shower, custom tile, quartz vanities, and oversized walk-in closet. Flex-room and additional bedrooms are perfectly placed throughout the home.
